description: Add eggs, spinach and tasty cheese to a baking dish for a speedy frittata that will keep little ones happy before dinner.
keywords: Frittata,Pescatarian,Seafood free,Gluten free,Tree nut free,Sesame free,Halal,Soy free,Wheat free,Vegetarian,Peanut free
name: Cheat's Frittata Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 5ml extra virgin olive oil cooking spray

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven to 220°C/200°C fan-forced. Spray a large 17cm x 24cm (4cm deep) baking dish with cooking spray.
Scatter spinach over base of greased dish. Bake for 5 minutes or until wilted.
Meanwhile, in a large bowl, whisk eggs until combined. Pour egg over spinach. Season with pepper. Sprinkle with cheese. Bake for 10 minute or until golden and cooked through. Slice to serve.
